AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622506> "The rate at which dead plant material (leaves, twigs, and other fine debris) is deposited onto the ground surface at a site."@en)
