AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622506> "litterfall rate"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622506> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622500>)

