AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622600> "An ecological variable that quantifies the frequency, intensity, or extent of a natural or anthropogenic disturbance acting on a site."@en)
