# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> (fire return interval)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> "The average length of time between successive fire events at a site."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> "2026-07-05T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> "fire frequency"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> "Distinct from fire frequency, which counts the number of fire events per unit time; the two are inversely related."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> "fire return interval"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622601> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622600>)

