AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622602> "A measure of the degree to which vegetation at a site is consumed or trampled by grazing animals over a specified period."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622602> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
