AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622602> "grazing intensity"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622602> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622600>)

