AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622702> "recruitment rate"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622702> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622700>)

