AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622708> "seedling emergence"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622708> "seedling emergence rate"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622708> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622704>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622709> (seedling height)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622709> "The vertical distance from the base of a seedling at soil level to its apical meristem or tallest leaf tip at the time of measurement."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622709> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622709> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622709> "seedling height"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622709> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622704>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> (seedling natural regeneration density)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> "The number of naturally regenerating seedlings per unit ground area at a site, arising without direct planting or seeding by humans."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> "natural regeneration density"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> "seedling regeneration"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> "seedling natural regeneration density"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622710> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622704>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622711> (height growth increment)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622711> "The increase in height of a tree or seedling over a specified time period, used as a measure of vertical growth performance."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622711> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622711> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622711> "height growth"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622711> "height growth increment"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622711> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622704>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622712> (root sucker density)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622712> "The number of root suckers — shoots arising from adventitious buds on the lateral roots or root collar of a parent plant — per unit ground area at a site over a specified monitoring period."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622712> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
