AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622712> "root sucker density"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622712> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622704>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> (water table depth)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> "The vertical distance from the ground surface to the upper boundary of the saturated zone in the soil or peat at a site."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> "water table level"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> "water table position"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> "Positive values indicate the water table is below ground surface; a value of zero indicates the water table is at the surface; negative values indicate inundation. Also reported as water table level relative to a fixed datum."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> "water table depth"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622713> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622200>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> (light availability)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> "The amount of photosynthetically active radiation reaching a specified position such as the forest floor or understory, typically expressed as a proportion of above-canopy incident radiation or as an absolute flux density."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> "light penetration"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> "understory light"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> "light availability"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622714> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622001>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> (Sphagnum cover)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> "The proportion of ground area at a peatland site covered by living Sphagnum mosses."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> "Sphagnum regeneration"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> "Sphagnum cover is the standard measured quantity at a point in time; the term 'Sphagnum regeneration' is commonly used in the peatland restoration literature to refer to the same phenomenon, particularly when framing it as a post-restoration outcome."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> "Sphagnum cover"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622715> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622301>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622716> (microbial biomass)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622716> "The mass of living microbial cells (bacteria, fungi, and other microorganisms) per unit mass or volume of soil at a site."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622716> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622716> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622716> "soil microbial biomass"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622716> "microbial biomass"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622716> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622500>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> (vegetation cover)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> "The proportion of ground area at a site covered by the combined foliage and stems of all vascular plant growth forms including trees, shrubs, and herbaceous plants."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> "plant cover"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> "total vegetation cover"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> "Encompasses canopy cover (ELMO:3622302), shrub cover (ELMO:3622309), herbaceous cover (ELMO:3622310), and understory cover (ELMO:3622308) as narrower terms. Use this term when reporting total across-strata plant cover."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> "vegetation cover"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622717> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622301>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> (competition intensity)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> "A measure of the degree to which neighbouring plants reduce the growth, survival, or reproductive output of target plants at a site over a specified period."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasBroadSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> "competitive pressure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> "competition"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> "competition intensity"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622718> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622600>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> (time since restoration)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> "The elapsed time between the initiation of a restoration intervention at a site and the point of ecological measurement, used to characterize the site along a recovery trajectory."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> "post-restoration age"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> "restoration age"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> "time since restoration"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622719> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622300>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622720> (restoration success index)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622720> "A composite measure evaluating the degree to which a restoration site has achieved specified ecological targets relative to a reference condition, assessed across one or more criteria such as species composition, structural complexity, or ecosystem function."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622720> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622720> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622720> "restoration success"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622720> "restoration success index"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622720> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622300>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800> (ecological process variable)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800> "An ecological variable that describes the rate, stage, or trajectory of a natural ecological process occurring at a site."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
