AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasRelatedSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800> "ecological dynamics variable"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800> "ecological process variable"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622300>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> (succession stage)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> "A categorical or ordinal characterization of the stage of ecological succession at a site, based on the composition and structure of the plant community relative to a reference successional trajectory."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasBroadSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> "successional stage"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> "succession"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> "succession stage"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622801> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622802> (natural regeneration rate)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622802> "The rate at which native vegetation re-establishes at a site through unassisted ecological processes, without direct planting or seeding by humans, over a specified period."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622802> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622802> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622802> "natural recovery"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622802> "natural regeneration rate"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622802> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622803> (regeneration failure rate)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622803> "The proportion of a site or planting cohort in which natural or assisted plant regeneration fails to achieve a specified establishment threshold over a monitoring period."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622803> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#creation_date> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622803> "2026-07-07T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622803> "regeneration failure"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622803> "regeneration failure rate"@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622803> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622800>)

# Class: <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622804> (habitat loss area)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622804> "The area of habitat lost to anthropogenic disturbance, land-use change, or ecological degradation within a specified landscape unit over a defined time period."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#created_by> <https://w3id.org/elmo/elmo_3622804> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1296-2528>)
